description:
Could this be an even better Better Sweater? This full zip version uses a hybrid fabric that withstands wear and repeated washings and still looks sharp. It's dyed with a low-impact process that significantly reduces the use of dyestuffs, energy and water compared to conventional dyeing methods.  A stand-up collar adds warmth and the zipper garage keeps it hospitable next the your chin when you zip it up fully. The shape and seams give it a streamlined shape that layers well and the zippered pockets stash your phone or keys.Made of warm, midweight polyester fleece.Raglan sleeves, princess seams on back, and forward seams on front for contoured shape and fit.Full-length zipper has a wind flap and kissing-welt closure.Pockets: zippered handwarmers, plus 2 interior drop-in pockets and one on the left arm.Polyester jersey trim on hood, cuffs, hem, pocket openings and wind flap.Seams are set forward in front with princess seaming in back.Hip length for warm coverage.

